Directed by Chaitanya Kumbhakonum.

Written by Arunabh Kumar. Shreyansh Pandey. Shivankit Singh Parihar. Shivankit Singh Parihar. Shivankit Singh Parihar. Harish Peddinti.

Cast  Badri Chavan( Aussie). Rahul Tewari( Alok). Karishma Singh( Gargi). Brij Bhushan Shukla( Rajesh Bhaiya). Abhishek Pandey( Nagu Man 1). Vaibhav Shukla( Deepak). Prashant Singh( Anant Pratap Singh). Suraj Rikame( Arshad). Aparajita Bajaj( Madhu). Anandeshwar Dwivedi( Nagu Bhaiya). Puneet Batra( Gopwani). Vivaan Karan( Gulli). Aman Jain( Bhaiyu). Alankrit Duggal( Vikas). Shashank Kadam( Sarthak). Shubhangi Latkar( Nikku’s Mother). Kunal Pant( Sanjay Soni). Ankit Motghare( Commentator). Ranjeet Kaushal( Commentator). Gaurav Singh( Shanu). Purnendu Bhattacharya( KK Shukla). Gulshan Nain( Jalwar). Lalitam Anand( Rohan). K.C. Shankar( Muddasar Khan). Onima Kashyap( Urvashi). Prakhar Sharma( Sonu). Gaurav Salvi( Lokesh). Abhishake Jha( Photogrpaher). Vipul Mayank( Prajapati). Vinod Bika( Gym Trainer). Vishal Naik( Gym Manager)

Language Hindi.

Producers Syed Zaid Ali. Zohaib Ali. Anandeshwar Dwivedi. Akshit Grover. Vijay Koshy. Arun Kumar. Arunabh Kumar. Chaitanya Kumbhakonum. Prajesh Mishra. Shreyansh Pandey. Mrinal Pant. Shivani Sinha. Pranav Thakker.

Production Contagious Online Media Network.

Creator Arunabh Kumar. Shreyansh Pandey. Shivankit Singh Parihar.

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 6

Status OnGoing (2022–)
